(PALEOMAP Project, www. earthbyte.org/paleomap-paleoatlas-for-gplates) and reprojected into Aitov projection(EPSG 53043) using QGIS. The palaeolatitude was calculated using the R package chronosphere (

, GPL license) including multiple models (

